### ============================================================
### Subscription Plans — Seed via API
### ============================================================
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Backend running on localhost:3030
###   2. System admin token — login as system_admin user first
###   3. Replace PASTE_TOKEN_HERE with the accessToken
###
### These plans match the Helena Coaching pricing structure.
### All prices in cents (CAD). 0 = custom/unlimited.
### Run each request top-to-bottom (### separates requests).
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3030/api
@token = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### ── Login as System Admin ──────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:3030/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@headsoft.net",
  "password": "HeadSoftAdmin2024!"
}

### ============================================================
### CONFLICT INTELLIGENCE (sortOrder 10–12)
### ============================================================

### CI-01: Conflict Intelligence — Starter ($599/mo, 50 users)
POST {{baseUrl}}/plans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "key": "ci-starter",
  "name": "Conflict Intelligence — Starter",
  "description": "Conflict Intelligence for teams up to 50 employees. AI-powered conflict analysis with manager conversation guides.",
  "priceMonthly": 59900,
  "overagePriceCents": 1500,
  "maxUsers": 50,
  "modules": ["conflict"],
  "limits": {
    "maxAIAnalyses": 10,
    "maxSurveyResponses": 500,
    "maxCoachingSessions": 0,
    "maxFileStorageMB": 500
  },
  "features": [
    "Up to 50 employees",
    "Conflict Intelligence module",
    "10 AI conflict analyses per month",
    "Manager conversation guides",
    "Risk score dashboard",
    "Email support"
  ],
  "isActive": true,
  "sortOrder": 10
}

