### ============================================================
### UTILITY: List all plans (verify seeding)
### ============================================================

### List all plans (system admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans/admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List active plans only (any authenticated user)
GET {{baseUrl}}/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
